  <brief_title>Determination of the &quot;Tissue Transit Time&quot; (TTT)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Determination of the &quot;Tissue Transit Time&quot; (TTT) in the MAG3-Tc99 Diuretic Renogram for Risk Stratification of Infants With Ureteropelvic Junction Obstruction - a Multicentric Prospective Observational Study</official_title>
